description: Support to Acceleration of the MDG Achievement in Indonesia

subproject.corporate outcome: Capacities of national and local institutions enhanced to scale up proven MDG acceleration interventions and to plan, monitor, report and evaluate the MDG progress in the context of related national development priorities
subproject.description:
Support to the acceleration of MDG Achievement in Indonesia - with expected outputs:
(1) Strategy and mechanisms to implement the MDG Roadmap are developed
(2) National and sub-national capacities improved to monitor, evaluate, analyse and report on MDGs and human development
(3) Project Document on Support to the Acceleration of MDG Achievement in Indonesia Finalised
subproject.title: Support acceleration MDGs Indo

title: SUPPORT TO THE ACCELERATION OF MDG ACHIEVEMENT IN INDONE
